<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Big bites</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --skin-tone-light: #f2d6c1;
            --dark-yellow: #ffcc00; 
            --dark-green: #004d00; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[var(--skin-tone-light)] text-gray-900 flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="bg-[var(--dark-green)] text-[var(--dark-yellow)] p-4 shadow-md">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold">Big bites</a>
            <div>
                <a href="/" class="hover:underline px-4">Home</a>
                <a href="/about" class="hover:underline px-4">About Us</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="hover:underline px-4">Contact Us</a>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="/logout" class="hover:underline px-4">Logout</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/login" class="hover:underline px-4">Login</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    

    <main class="flex-grow p-4">
        <div class="w-full max-w-2xl bg-white text-gray-900 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">About Us</h1>
            <p class="mb-4">At Big bites, we are proud to have a talented web development team dedicated to creating exceptional digital experiences. Our team combines creativity, technical expertise, and a passion for innovation to deliver top-notch solutions.</p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to build engaging, user-friendly, and high-performance websites and applications. We focus on delivering solutions that not only meet but exceed our clients' expectations, driving their success in the digital world.</p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Meet the Team</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <img src="/images/Riddhi.jpeg" alt="Ridhhi Mistry" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Riddhi Mistry</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Lead Developer</p>
                        <p>Riddhi leads our development team with a wealth of experience in building scalable and efficient web applications. She specializes in backend development and system architecture.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <img src="/images/vishaw.jpeg" alt="Vishwa Lad" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Vishwa Lad</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Front-End Developer</p>
                        <p>Vishwa is our front-end expert, creating stunning and intuitive user interfaces. She is passionate about making web experiences accessible and visually engaging.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <img src="/images/mansi.jpeg" alt="Mansi Bhojak" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Mansi Bhojak</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">UI/UX Designer</p>
                        <p>Mansi designs delightful user experiences and interfaces, ensuring our applications are not only functional but also aesthetically pleasing. Her work focuses on user-centered design.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
